Melted Vader Keycap

I don’t care for most artisan keycaps, but a keycap of Vader’s mask as seen in The Force Awakens was a must have.

A group buy for this keycap came and went on Massdrop this morning. I was lucky enough to have snatched one up before they were all gone.

It won’t arrive until February, but it should go nicely with my Originative Carbon Black keycaps.

Typed on Octopage

Morgan 2015-12-22 KEYBOARDS
